Product Description

Elevate your bathroom experience with Good Housekeeping’s Yorkshire Bathroom Exhaust Fan, designed with the utmost care and attention to detail. This fan effortlessly complements your existing decor, infusing your space with a touch of elegance and luxury. Featuring 2.5 Sones and airflow of 80 CFM, bid farewell to excess moisture and unwelcome odors. The Good Housekeeping Yorkshire Bathroom Exhaust Fan is here to transform your bathroom into the serene spa retreat you've always envisioned, offering you the indulgence you truly deserve.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Aaron Dunnuck
3.0 out of 5 stars Looks good, but the installation is a nightmare.
Reviewed in the United States on May 17, 2023
Color: Matte BlackVerified Purchase
This light/fan combo looks and operates properly. However due to its large weight and size it's installation is very difficult. the way that the light mounts to the box is 4 screws that come down from the fan. but they are very short and if the box isn't mounted perfectly flush with the ceiling then they won't extend far enough down to mount the actual light fixture. I had to buy new screws that were longer to properly mount the actual light fixture. The plastic vent ouptut mount also is located very close to the bottom of the electrical box which means that if the drywall is over 1/2 in thick you won't be able to flush mount it due to the added bulk of the 4" vent hose. All in all the installation of this was a nightmare. Now that it is done it's exactally what we wanted. But be warned the installation is significanly more difficult than a normal light/fan combo.
